{
  "text": "This descriptive study was done in two stages. First, a systematic literature search was carried out to recognize the articles to be taken in the study. Then, the quality of the studies was evaluated with STROBE. This study keeps the recommendations of the PRISMA statement for its reporting [CITATION_1] .",
